Ex parte: In the Matter of Arthur Hewett and Tom A. Keating, Petitioners. Motion sub*625mitted January 24, 1910. Decided March 14, 1910. The Attorney General and The Solicitor General for the respondent.

Motion for leave to file a petition for a writ of habeas corpus denied. Mr. Thos. F. Gatts for the petitioner.
